    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                <date>Elul 9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5589</date>
            </p>
            <p>To <addressee>Messrs Joseph S. Cohen</addressee> &amp;<lb/>
                <addressee>S. M. Goldsmidt</addressee></p>
            <p rend="align(center)">committee in behalf of the K. K. M. Israel.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Gentlemen.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Permit me to transmit through you to the members of<lb/> the K. K.
                M. I. my acceptance of the office of Hazan, to which office<lb/> they did me the
                honour to elect me on yesterday. In accepting this<lb/> highly responsible station I
                am fully alive to the various, and in a<lb/> measure, new duties, which devolve on
                me. No man <add>can be</add> more <add>aware</add> than my-<lb/>self, <del>can be
                    aware</del> of my want of qualifications to acquit myself pro-<lb/>perly; but it
                shall be my constant aim, to merit the indulgence if<lb/> not the confidence of this
                respectable congregation, but attending strictly<lb/> as far as lies in my power, to
                the duties of my office, so that I may<lb/> never be accused of carelessness and
                negligence. It would be unbecoming<lb/> in me to be more particular, as I do not
                consider it right to make<lb/> promises, which I might be unable to
                    <sic>fulfil</sic>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Accept for yourself my sincere thanks for the highly flattering<lb/>
                manner in which you announced to me the result of the election;<lb/> and be assured,
                that your prosperity and the prosperity of the com-<lb/>munity you represent, will
                ever be gratifying</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">to your and the congregation's</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">very obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)"><persName role="author">Isaac Leeser</persName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">May God preserve you!</p>
        </body>
    </text>
